<HEADLINE> Rwandan Army Kills 6 Militiamen in Operation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, February 7 (Xinhua) -- The Rwandan army killed six
Hutu militiamen in operations in Kinigi, north of Ruhengeri town
Friday, military sources said.
</P>
<P>
"There was an engagement with Hutu militias in Kagano sector
of Kinigi Friday," said Major Emmanuel Ndahiro, the army
spokesman, according to reports of Rwanda News Agency (RNA)
reaching here Saturday.
</P>
<P>
