<HEADLINE> Microsoft Eyes Market in Uganda </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, February 7 (Xinhua) -- Microsoft, the world's leading
software manufacturer, intends to expand its market in Uganda
through local partnership.
</P>
<P>
Louis Otieno, Microsoft regional business development manager,
said at a conference in Kampala Thursday that his company "is
seriously eyeing this market."
</P>
<P>
The economic performance indicators and the business potential
of Uganda are encouraging, Otieno said.
</P>
