markets with 50 percent of growth rate and half of the company's
sales last year, The New Vision paper said in its report.
</P>
<P>
Microsoft entered Africa five years ago and has established
offices in Indian Ocean islands, Zimbabwe, Kenya and South
Africa.
</P>
