Exchange (LME) would also set the mood on the KLTM, he added.
</P>
<P>
On the Malaysian rubber market this week, March RSS One ended
the week at 239.50 sen (62 U.S. cents) per kg from 336.00 sen (87
cents) last week while SMR 20 closed at 333.00 sen (86 cents) per
kg from last week's 337.00 sen (87.5 cents).
