Friday.
</P>
<P>
Yakovlev made the remark in reply to inquiries at the State
Duma, the lower house of the Russian Parliament. The lawmakers
raised questions about the reported possibility of a nuclear
attack launched by the United States against Iraq. They also asked
about Russia's defense capabilities.
</P>
<P>
The U.S. embassy in Moscow issued a denial on Wednesday that
Washington planned a nuclear attack.
</P>
<P>
