<HEADLINE> 6 Killed in Road Accident in Thailand </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, February (Xinhua) -- Six people were killed in a road
accident Friday in northeastern Thailand's province of Nakhon
Ratchasima, according to a report reaching here Saturday.
</P>
<P>
