carriers gathered in the region, ready to mount an attack on
Iraq once ordered.
</P>
<P>
the United States has gathered nearly 400 warplanes and some
20 warships in the region and has threatened along with Britain
to use military force against Iraq unless it agrees to full
weapons inspections under U.N. resolutions. 
